# cage

> Open an applications in a kiosk mode.
> More information: <https://github.com/cage-kiosk/cage/blob/master/cage.1.scd>.

- Run an application:

`cage {{application}}`

- Give the application arguments:

`cage -- {{application}} {{arguments}}`

- Display help:

`cage -h`
